Nothing of substance?  Bah, people have left EQ in droves because doing nothing but raid, raid, raid every expansion gets extremely old.  There are zero alternatives, human nature makes us want the very best for our character and in order to achieve those goals you have to raid endlessly.  <br>
<br>
There needs to be more variety in the high-end game or I believe this trend will just continue.  The majority of the friends I played with over the last five years have moved on from EQ, the endless series of raids simply burned them out.  More raids tuned around 54 people aren't going to bring them back.<br>
